snippet.title: Emerald Wasp [Horror Rpg | Trailer]
snippet.description:
Rassvet Ops was one of the most mysterious disappearences to these days. Now forgotten, the last survivor is hiding in the shadows...

Emerald Wasp is a Horror RPG game.
You can play it for free here:
https://banya.itch.io/emerald-wasp
